Package: fgczquartotemplate
Title: FGCZ Quarto Report Templates and Shared Styling
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Peter", "Leary", role = "aut"),
    person("Jonas", "Grossmann", role = "aut"),
    person("Falko", "Noé", role = "aut"),
    person("Witold", "Wolski", , "witold@ethz.ch", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: A shared Quarto format extension giving FGCZ analysis packages
    (ezRun, prolfqua, prolfquapp) one look and feel: an SCSS theme, an HTML
    header, tabset and figure styling, and an opt-in figure-finder toolbar.
    Add it with 'quarto add prolfqua/fgczquartotemplate' and select it with
    'format: fgczquartotemplate-html'.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/prolfqua/fgczquartotemplate,
    https://prolfqua.github.io/fgczquartotemplate/
